---
title: Korean-Inspired Veggie Bowls with Plant-Based Protein and Pickled Radishes
description: Our Korean-inspired bowls are made vegetarian-friendly using plant-based protein! Protein shreds are coated in a bold sauce that gets a little spice from gochujang. Tangy, quick-pickled radishes liven up the dish, while green onion adds herbaceous flair!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-veges-a-la-coreenne-24b2bed0.jpg
